OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FVariable
OL,6,Fcloud with some outbreaks of rain or
OL,7,Fshowers Friday, mainly on western
OL,8,Fhills. Brighter in the east. Breezy.
OL,9,FDry with sunny spells on Saturday and
OL,10,FSunday. Temperatures nearer average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
